TITLE: Accessing Nested Map Values with map.get() in Sass
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use map.get() to access deeply nested values in a map structure.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sass/sass-site/blob/main/source/documentation/modules/map.md#2025-04-09_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: scss
CODE:
```
@use "sass:map";

$config: (a: (b: (c: d)));
@debug map.get($config, a, b, c); // d
```

LANGUAGE: sass
CODE:
```
@use "sass:map"

$config: (a: (b: (c: d)))
@debug map.get($config, a, b, c) // d
```

