TITLE: Extracting Map Values in Sass
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates using the map.values() function to extract all values from a map into a comma-separated list. The example extracts font weight values from a map of font weight definitions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sass/sass-site/blob/main/source/documentation/modules/map.md#2025-04-09_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: scss
CODE:
```
@use "sass:map";

$font-weights: ("regular": 400, "medium": 500, "bold": 700);

@debug map.values($font-weights); // 400, 500, 700
```

LANGUAGE: sass
CODE:
```
@use "sass:map"

$font-weights: ("regular": 400, "medium": 500, "bold": 700)

@debug map.values($font-weights)  // 400, 500, 700
```

