TITLE: Accessing Nested Map Values with map.get() in Sass
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use map.get() to access values in nested maps, including handling of missing keys.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sass/sass-site/blob/main/source/documentation/modules/map.md#2025-04-09_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: scss
CODE:
```
@use "sass:map";

$fonts: (
  "Helvetica": (
    "weights": (
      "regular": 400,
      "medium": 500,
      "bold": 700
    )
  )
);

@debug map.get($fonts, "Helvetica", "weights", "regular"); // 400
@debug map.get($fonts, "Helvetica", "colors"); // null
```

LANGUAGE: sass
CODE:
```
@use "sass:map"

$fonts: ("Helvetica": ("weights": ("regular": 400, "medium": 500, "bold": 700)))

@debug map.get($fonts, "Helvetica", "weights", "regular") // 400
@debug map.get($fonts, "Helvetica", "colors") // null
```

