TITLE: Iterating Through Maps with @each in Sass
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use the @each rule to iterate through each key-value pair in a Sass map. The example creates a set of utility classes for different text colors.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sass/sass-site/blob/main/source/documentation/values/maps.md#2025-04-09_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: scss
CODE:
