$theme-colors: (
  "success": #28a745,
  "info": #17a2b8,
  "warning": #ffc107,
);

@each $name, $color in $theme-colors {
  .alert-#{$name} {
    color: $color;
    background-color: lighten($color, 40%);
  }
}
```

LANGUAGE: sass
CODE:
```
$theme-colors: ("success": #28a745, "info": #17a2b8, "warning": #ffc107)

@each $name, $color in $theme-colors
  .alert-#{$name}
    color: $color
    background-color: lighten($color, 40%)
```

